  <h3 class="info">Blogs and Posts</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <div calss="container">
      <p>User can post their queries in this section. All the posts or question by any users is dumped in this section. Users can take part 
      in answering the question of their preference.</p>
      <p>While user ask a question, it is essential that they ensure the questions clarity. Orignial poster of the question is expected to 
      well structure and proof read their posts before posting. In case of ambiguity and unclarity of the question, original poster of the event 
