  <h3 class="info">Votes and Score.</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <div calss="container">
      <p>
        Users in the portal can upvote and down vote posts and answers based on the relevancy of the event. You may down cast a vote if 
        you find a post ambigous or unclear. You may up vote a post if you find it relevant. you can not vote on your own behalf 
        for any events by you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Users are expected to use the voting system based on the relevancy of an event. A vote on a post would yield 1 score to the original 
        poster. Accpeted answers would yield a <b>TEN</b> point for the user. So users may answer wisely and relevantly.
      </p>

    </div>
